{
  "stem": "20088.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And each time we traveled through the villages and the train stopped, first the Poles and later the Russian farmer's women came onto the trucks to bargain with us if we had something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were selling eggs or chicken or-- and they wanted goods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Textiles, scarves, blankets, clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we did have bits and pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we did swap it for all kind of food again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Always food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] and so we traveled to-- many, many days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes we were weeks on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when we stopped they told us we can get out and we didn't like to go on the bucket in the train, so we went always outside at the railway side.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother was outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say-- we were all outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly the train slowly started to move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we all-- it was high, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we all tried to clamber in and something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother didn't so quickly and the train started to speed up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all put our hands on, tried to get her up, but she couldn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the train left and she was left behind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was terribly upset, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but, I mean, there was nothing you could do about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next place was a channel, which it was Romania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there again we went into that town and we left in an old school building or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went out into the town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went into Jewish houses when there was a mezuzah, because the Romanians, a lot of them have not been transported.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of Romanian Jews survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
